For additional information about the repository, please see the
README in the repository top-level.

Author: Nicolas Marchildon

Description:

Reports the number of web server error response codes

This script can be called by Apache by setting up a special logger:

   LogFormat "%>s" status_only
   CustomLog "|/path/to/apache-logs-to-ganglia.pl -d 10" status_only

Language: Perl

Category: Services::HTTP

Dependencies: Getopt::Long
